headline: BIO Q4 Earnings and Revenues Miss Estimates, Stock Down Aftermarket
summary: Bio-Rad witnesses growth across the Clinical Diagnostics segment in the fourth quarter, primarily driven by an increased demand for quality control and blood typing products.
